extendedInfo.description: FIND YOUR NEAREST PALM SPRINGS, COACHELLA VALLEY SUNLINE BUS ROUTE MAPS AND SCHEDULESFed up of not knowing when the next bus is coming? Just missed a bus and need to know if its worth waiting for the next one? Need to know where the nearest bus stop is?If your like thousands of other people in the Coachella Valley you need answers to these questions then look no further than the "Coachella Valley Sunline Bus Routes" app for Android phones and tablets.Features:* Route Maps for all Coachella Valley Sunline buses, including Palm Springs, Desert Hot Springs, Rancho Mirage, Cathedral City, Palm Desert, Indian Wells, Bermuda Dunes, Indio, La Quinta, Coachella, and Mecca areas.* Never lean over anyone at the bus stop again.* No more squinting in the dark reading map.* Up to the minute information on all bus arrivals via quick link to online tracker* Ability to quick share your current location via text, email, social media...* Every bus route easily at your fingertips and stored on your phoneIn order to keep the app 100% free, you will receive the following âSearch shortcut icon on your home screen,Search shortcut on your bookmarks and browser homepage.This will help us bring you more cool apps like this in the future.You can delete the search shortcuts easily (Drag & Drop to the garbage), this will not affect the application in any way.Keywords: Palm Springs, Coachella Valley, bus, Sunline, live, tracking, service, times, routes, travel, schedule, buses, bus stops

reviews.title: Not a useful app...
reviews.comment: Google Maps has a transit option that works much better than this. This app just has an interface that ties into the Sunline website. Don\'t waste your time or storage on this one.
reviews.author: J Ponik

reviews.title: Great
reviews.comment: No issue with ads, it clearly states in the description what it does
reviews.author: mike roemelen

reviews.title: Ad infested
reviews.comment: Dont get unless you dont mind ads pop ups every 10 minutes
reviews.author: Roberto galvez
